title: The West Palm Beach Roast Session With D.C.Young Fly Karlous Miller & Chico Bean Part1 | Ep. 130
itunes:title: The West Palm Beach Roast Session With D.C.Young Fly Karlous Miller & Chico Bean Part1 | Ep. 130
description:
The 85 South Show crew returned to The West Palm Beach improv for the second time, roasting an all-new audience. It's The 85 South Show so you know everybody in the front row get's roasted...and we always have to shout out the rappers in the audience. T.I., Bonecrusher and more have shown up to The 85 South Show and this week it's "Loose Change" " D.C. Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean hold nothing back and drop all new hilarious freestyles live from Florida. Stand- up comedy, roasting, freestyle comedy - only the 85 South Show can do it like this!
